tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE chat_transcripts (
    chat_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    chat_date DATE,
    chat_text TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE VideoCallLogs (
  call_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID NOT NULL,
  call_datetime TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  call_duration INTERVAL NOT NULL,
  call_type VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE ConsultationDetails (
  consultation_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID NOT NULL,
  consultation_datetime TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  consultation_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  consultation_notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE video_call_logs (
    call_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    call_duration INTERVAL,
    call_type VARCHAR(50),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE consultation_details (
    consultation_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    chat_id UUID,
    call_id UUID,
    user_id UUID,
    start_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    end_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE chat_transcripts (
    transcript_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID NOT NULL,
    consultant_id UUID NOT NULL,
    transcript_text TEXT NOT NULL,
    transcript_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE video_call_logs (
    call_log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID NOT NULL,
    consultant_id UUID NOT NULL,
    call_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    call_duration INTERVAL NOT NULL,
    call_type VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE consultations (
    consultation_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID NOT NULL,
    consultant_id UUID NOT NULL,
    consultation_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    consultation_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
);
